"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 19.425px; font-family: Calibri, Calibri_MSFontService, sans-serif; color: rgb(66, 66, 66);\"><span class=\"EOP SCXW137846560 BCX0\" data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 19.425px; font-family: Consolas, Consolas_MSFontService, monospace;\"><span class=\"EOP SCXW235355509 BCX0\" data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 19.425px; font-family: Helvetica;\">Terimakasih&nbsp;</span></span><span data-contrast=\"auto\" class=\"TextRun SCXW138083308 BCX0\" xml:lang=\"ID-ID\" lang=\"ID-ID\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Consolas, Consolas_MSFontService, monospace; font-kerning: none; line-height: 19.425px; font-variant-ligatures: none !important;\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW138083308 BCX0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: Helvetica;\">telah membaca tulisan ini, semoga bermanfaat untuk rekan – rekan semua.</span></span></span><br></p>','296fe964d6e6e8ecc4c17e18d09b6e1da4ed8804.jpg','php laravel','anang novriadi','2019-06-10 05:43:28','2019-06-10 07:27:12'),(5,2,'CRUD (Create Read Update Delete) Laravel + UI Kit','crud-laravel-ui-kit','<p><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">﻿</span><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: #1d2129;\">Halo, berjumpa lagi dengan posting saya yang akan membahas cara membuat create, update, read/view dan delete dengan laravel dan ui kit.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica;\">Jika kalian belum tau cara untuk instalasi laravel nya, kalian bisa cek pada link ini untuk petunjuk penginstallanya.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: #1d2129;\">Yuk lansung saja ke topik dan langkah - langkahnya.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: #1d2129;\">Siapkan project laravel yang sudah terinstall dan set file .env, jika belum ada kalian tinggal tinggal copy paste dari .env.example dan buat file dengan nama .env</span><br></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<style type=\"text/css\">\r\np.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 12.0px \'Helvetica Neue\'; color: #454545}\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"p1\"><script src=\"https://gist.github.com/anangnovriadi/d1b59a2fbebab1f83a34ee32de3ca705.js\"></script></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: #1d2129;\">Buat file migration dengan command berikut.</span></p><p><b><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: #1d2129;\">php artisan make:migration create_books_table</span></b></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: #1d2129;\">Sisipkan code berikut pada file migration yang sudah dibuat tadi pada folder </span><b><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: #1d2129;\">database/migration/create_books_table.php</span></b></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<style type=\"text/css\">\r\np.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 12.0px \'Helvetica Neue\'; color: #454545}\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"p1\"><script src=\"https://gist.github.com/anangnovriadi/3ef9be74ed43a7202d3d6f98ca3588e0.js\"></script></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: #1d2129;\">Tambahkan code berikut pada file <b>app/Providers/</b></span><font face=\"Helvetica\"><b style=\"color: #1d2129;\">AppServiceProvider.php</b></font></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<style type=\"text/css\">\r\np.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 12.0px \'Helvetica Neue\'; color: #454545}\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"p1\"><script src=\"https://gist.github.com/anangnovriadi/d45e46346048091591fa3edc26f8cf0b.js\"></script></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: #1d2129;\">Jalankan command berikut untuk migrasi ke database mysql.</span></p><p><b><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: #1d2129;\">php artisan migrate</span></b></p><p><font color=\"#1d2129\" face=\"Helvetica\">Setelah berhasil melakukan migrasi ke database, kalian dapat menjalankan command untuk membuat model dan controller pada laravel. Pada laravel kalian dimudahkan dalam membuat sebuah controller maupun model dengan hanya satu baris perintah. Jalankan command untuk membuat model dan controller book.</font></p><p><font color=\"#1d2129\" face=\"Helvetica\"><b>php artisan make:controller BookControoller</b></font></p><p><font color=\"#1d2129\" face=\"Helvetica\"><b>php artisan make:model Book</b></font></p><p><font color=\"#1d2129\" face=\"Helvetica\">Siapkan route nya. pada <b>routes/web.php</b></font></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<style type=\"text/css\">\r\np.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 12.0px \'Helvetica Neue\'; color: #454545}\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"p1\"><script src=\"https://gist.github.com/anangnovriadi/f6b7ec2c074f1f9757b7324deb68f4fa.js\"></script></p><p><font color=\"#1d2129\" face=\"Helvetica\">Let\'s write code, pada <b>app/Http/Controllers/BookController.php</b></font></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<style type=\"text/css\">\r\np.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 12.0px \'Helvetica Neue\'; color: #454545}\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"p1\"><script src=\"https://gist.github.com/anangnovriadi/3e6e735f04259347646dd51e5658fe0e.js\"></script></p><p><font color=\"#1d2129\" face=\"Helvetica\">Selanjutnya pada model. <b>app/Book.php</b></font></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<style type=\"text/css\">\r\np.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 12.0px \'Helvetica Neue\'; color: #454545}\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"p1\"><script src=\"https://gist.github.com/anangnovriadi/f507aa3a18df3b7ecd24204c0828e57a.js\"></script></p><p><font color=\"#1d2129\" face=\"Helvetica\">Selanjutnya kita main di blade templates untuk memudahkan dalam memisahkan bagian antara layout dan content, blade yang sudah disediakan oleh laravel sangat kompleks dan mudah untuk digunakan.</font></p><p><font color=\"#1d2129\" face=\"Helvetica\"><b>resources/views/layout/app.blade.php</b></font></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<style type=\"text/css\">\r\np.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 12.0px \'Helvetica Neue\'; color: #454545}\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"p1\"><script src=\"https://gist.github.com/anangnovriadi/b708c100dacbe15a5c819c54271fa1b8.js\"></script></p><p><font color=\"#1d2129\" face=\"Helvetica\"><b>resources/views/layout/header.php</b></font></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<style type=\"text/css\">\r\np.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 12.0px \'Helvetica Neue\'; color: #454545}\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"p1\"><script src=\"https://gist.github.com/anangnovriadi/0724adf1051c06c4af3d50b757bcc27f.js\"></script></p><p><font color=\"#1d2129\" face=\"Helvetica\"><b>resources/views/home.blade.php</b></font></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<style type=\"text/css\">\r\np.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 12.0px \'Helvetica Neue\'; color: #454545}\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"p1\"><script src=\"https://gist.github.com/anangnovriadi/c9461b8425f6d218fe7ecd6cb71924c7.js\"></script></p><p><font color=\"#1d2129\" face=\"Helvetica\"><b>resources/views/add.blade.php</b></font></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<style type=\"text/css\">\r\np.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 12.0px \'Helvetica Neue\'; color: #454545}\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"p1\"><script src=\"https://gist.github.com/anangnovriadi/6c1462152c7a2234b92db90a34abfa02.js\"></script></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<style type=\"text/css\">\r\np.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 12.0px \'Helvetica Neue\'; color: #454545}\r\n</style>\r\n</p><p><font color=\"#1d2129\" face=\"Helvetica\"><b>resources/views/edit.blade.php</b></font></p>\r\n<p></p><p class=\"p1\"><script src=\"https://gist.github.com/anangnovriadi/5939235029e9f5ba68781af61c0e60ab.js\"></script></p>\r\n\r\n<p><font color=\"#1d2129\" face=\"Helvetica\"><br></font></p><p><font color=\"#1d2129\" face=\"Helvetica\">Terimakasih telah membaca tutorial singkat ini, semoga bermanfaat.</font></p><p><font color=\"#1d2129\" face=\"Helvetica\">untuk project lengkapnya silahkan menuju link berikut&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/anangnovriadi/laravel-crud-ui-kit\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/anangnovriadi/laravel-crud-ui-kit</a></font></p>','b1b14dac48bbeb0cd3e0d45e34f0ba1c829d9424.jpg','php laravel ui','anang novriadi','2019-06-13 09:46:11','2019-06-20 16:38:57');
